description: Play as Sunny, an adorable tanuki with the power to walk back and forth through time, as she helps her friends prepare for each season's final days. Going back in time is as easy as turning around and walking back to where you came from, and everything you do can be undone at any time.
name: Seasonspree
intro: A cozy time-nudging adventure on a tiny planet full of adorable animal friends. Walk through time in both directions as you help your friends celebrate the passing of each season!
